{"tid":640869,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【南海風雲】美太平洋司令揚言武力阻中國 華媒寸爆：𢱑軍費","createTime":"2018-04-24T15:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T08:50:17.000Z","uid":141151,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"21933478ada9e297c75c640f82e2cac8f94ab72d","tid":640869,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:02:17.000Z","msg":"【南海風雲】美太平洋司令揚言武力阻中國 華媒寸爆：𢱑軍費<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180422/58104670\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F58104670&d=as9LQJ0q1zqmooOgAV5qMOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=60c3910c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F58104670&h=c5024570\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180422/58104670</a><br />\n<br />\n中國媒體今日援引美國《新聞周刊》的報道，指美軍候任太平洋司令部司令菲利普&middot;戴維森（Philip S. Davidson），日前向國會提交報告，大肆渲染中國的「軍事威脅」，並揚言「要想阻止中國控制南海」，只有訴諸「武裝衝突」這一條路。<br />\n<br />\n《新聞周刊》報道指，被任命為新任美軍太平洋司令部司令的菲利普&middot;戴維森，20日向參議院軍事委員會提交了一份書面報告，力陳中國的「軍事威脅」，並指中國的軍事力量已經強大到足以支撐其在南海的領土主張，而要想「阻止中國」，只有進行「武裝衝突」這一條路。<br />\n<br />\n戴維森聲稱，「中國在亞太地區不停擴大軍事部署，修建秘密軍事基地」，「解放軍已經有徹底掌控該地區的能力，南海其他國家無法與之爭奪」，並指「一旦中國完全佔領南海，中國就可以將其影響力擴大到數千英里之外，深入大洋洲」，「解放軍可以以此為據點，挑戰美國在該區域的軍事存在，輾壓任何其他聲索國的軍力。」最後，他總結道，「如果美國不與中國進行『戰爭』，中國就一定有能力控制南海」。<br />\n<br />\n戴維森的這番言論，隨即引起中國媒體關注，並直斥這是一個他想像中「聳人聽聞」的未來。中國媒體並指，事實上，此前就有軍事專家指出，美軍類似的報告層出不窮，目的很簡單&mdash;&mdash;向美國國會要錢。然而希望美國國會為軍隊撥款並不是一件容易的事，所以渲染中國軍隊的發展，大肆誇大並營造「中國威脅論」的氣氛，就成了一大「捷徑」。<br />\n<br />\n報道還揶揄，美軍負責人指摘中國的同時，卻忘了「到底是誰不停在南海攪局」，「近一段時間以來，中國與南海周邊國家關係總體向好發展，這令美方頗為不爽，採取一系列行為『秀存在感』」。<br />\n<br />\n海外網<br />\n<br />\n中国又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f2af6076b8c721f87d3aa69ad610029cd63959","tid":640869,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58ff7152a67d0c2da2e19968f03a847d01c8abc","tid":640869,"uid":76245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又羸"},{"pid":"18375f97caed1d2327f7a802e64e53e2eb130a01","tid":640869,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T22:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86295d9abf3b1464f2edaeeab9e3c009412a5cce","tid":640869,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T22:47:52.000Z","msg":"贏國好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c7673507c37c4a91c75501d5acc5a6c1df94c6","tid":640869,"uid":132859,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T22:57:03.000Z","msg":"到底是誰不停在南海建人工島？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3431c3bb04c8e692de4139df5039fc9c731af46f","tid":640869,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T23:09:39.000Z","msg":"到時美軍打了南海島自用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f93028fa37fd64f649264940c85d39d109b5fe","tid":640869,"uid":60333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T23:10:46.000Z","msg":"咁算唔算間接認自己廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6d5fa39915689e0b01b4a3471bb35bd9075eee","tid":640869,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T23:21:40.000Z","msg":"到底是誰不停在南海攪局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d05b34e3f604d0700b8eb650290cfb8bd32114d","tid":640869,"uid":8187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T23:32:53.000Z","msg":"再贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg