/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07111b963b3d49140b7cf2993c137c0898c161c3","tid":640869,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T00:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b53ecd54b54c269677142aa8e6cba3115d569cc","tid":640869,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T00:20:11.000Z","msg":"China installs cruise missiles on South China Sea outposts: CNBC<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-southchinasea-china-missiles/china-installs-cruise-missiles-on-south-china-sea-outposts-cnbc-report-idUSKBN1I336G?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-southchinasea-china-missiles%2Fchina-installs-cruise-missiles-on-south-china-sea-outposts-cnbc-report-idUSKBN1I336G%3F&d=as9LQJ0q1zqmooOgAV5qMOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=a4dd6246\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-southchinasea-china-missiles%2Fchina-installs-cruise-missiles-on-south-china-sea-outposts-cnbc-report-idUSKBN1I336G%3F&h=11a451f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-southchinasea-china-missiles/china-installs-cruise-missiles-on-south-china-sea-outposts-cnbc-report-idUSKBN1I336G?</a><br />\n<br />\nWASHINGTON (Reuters) - China has installed anti-ship cruise missiles and surface-to-air missile systems on three of its outposts in the South China Sea, U.S. news network CNBC reported on Wednesday, citing sources with direct knowledge of U.S. intelligence reports.<br />\n<br />\nThe installations, if confirmed, would mark the first Chinese missile deployments in the Spratly Islands, where several Asian countries including Vietnam and Taiwan have rival claims.<br />\n<br />\nChina has made no mention of any missile deployments but says its military facilities in the Spratlys are purely defensive, and that it can do what it likes on its own territory.<br />\n<br />\nCNBC quoted unnamed sources as saying that according to U.S. intelligence assessments, the missiles were moved to Fiery Cross Reef, Subi Reef and Mischief Reef within the past 30 days."},{"pid":"a78fa9ae21bdd2cb5e7ae767cf3a1450833829f5","tid":640869,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85918a07deb8bb7b094e61eb0b63d8bd5e9a6ca","tid":640869,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T19:59:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共匪</span></span>"},{"pid":"458d72f9b6fe2e62e9c6918e6c08ecd7e31bc375","tid":640869,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T00:12:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8dbd53b39300f83443b3125d4e27cdbb9188451","tid":640869,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T08:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}